ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Absolutely outstanding course! Interesting, challenging, engaging, with a wonderful reading list. You read everything from classic works to brilliant new monographs to insightful criticism. The work-load is not too onerous, and Prof. Pitti is a wonderful instructor!
Seminar with a relatively large scope that studies the histories of different communities of Latinos in the United States. I would wholeheartedly recommend it to other students in the future
